data.description:
Introducing your dream home! This fantastic 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom ranch-style residence is a perfect blend of comfort and functionality. Nestled on a spacious lot, the property boasts a large backyard adorned with two sheds, providing ample storage space for all your outdoor essentials.

Safety and peace of mind are top priorities, with radon mitigation already installed. The convenience continues with a brand-new sewer line and sidewalk, ensuring a hassle-free living experience. RV enthusiasts will appreciate the dedicated parking space, making it easy to accommodate your recreational vehicle.

Key updates include a newer roof, a modern water heater, and an efficient furnace – all contributing to a home that's not only aesthetically pleasing but also equipped for long-term durability and efficiency.

Don't miss the opportunity to make this residence your own, where every detail has been carefully considered to enhance your living experience. Welcome home to comfort, convenience, and quality living!
